    *   The staticConfig, defaultConfig and configSchema has been moved inside static block to take advantage of static block execution only once
    *   The validate method has been moved inside the constructor
    *   The getter and setter for config has been added
*   LifecycleEvent
    *   The event property is now a readonly property using the # symbol which means it can only be accessed within the class
*   LifecycleHandler
    *   Added the bind method that binds the handler to the target
    *   The execute method now uses the target
*   ComponentLifecycleHandler
    *   New class that is responsible for handling events
*   NexusCoreLifecycleEvent
    *   New class that is responsible for handling events with a lifecycle perspective
*   NexusCore
    *   Made the lifecycle private to prevent public manipulation
    *   The status property is now a getter and setter
    *   The onLifecycleEvent method now returns a new lifecycle event
    *   Added a private on method that is used for lifecycle event handling
    *   The executeLifecycleEvent method now uses the on method to handle the event
    *   The load and shutdown methods have been made async
    *   The start and stop methods have been added